<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>New Registration Alert</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2196f3 0%, #1976d2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 25px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .alert-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .alert-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd 0%, #bbdefb 100%);
            border: 2px solid #2196f3;
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .alert-box::before {
            content: "🔔";
            position: absolute;
            top: -15px;
            left: 50%;
            transform: translateX(-50%);
            background: #2196f3;
            color: white;
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .user-profile {
            background: white;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .user-type-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 5px 15px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .user-type-user {
            background: #e8f5e8;
            color: #138808;
        }
        
        .user-type-merchant {
            background: #fff3e0;
            color: #FF9933;
        }
        
        .user-details {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #2196f3;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .action-required {
            background: #ffebee;
            border: 2px solid #f44336;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .action-required h4 {
            color: #d32f2f;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .action-required p {
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 14px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        
        .cta-button.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2196f3 0%, #1976d2 100%);
            color: white;
        }
        
        .cta-button.secondary {
            background: white;
            color: #2196f3;
            border: 2px solid #2196f3;
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(33, 150, 243, 0.3);
        }
        
        .registration-summary {
            background: #f0f8f0;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #138808;
        }
        
        .registration-summary h4 {
            color: #138808;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .summary-stats {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(120px, 1fr));
            gap: 15px;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
        
        .stat-item {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 6px;
        }
        
        .stat-number {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #138808;
        }
        
        .stat-label {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                box-shadow: none;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 20px 15px;
            }
            
            .user-details {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
            
            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 250px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="alert-icon">👤</div>
            <h1>New Registration Alert</h1>
            <p>Action Required - User Approval</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 25px;">
                Hi {{adminName}},
            </p>
            
            <div class="alert-box">
                <h2 style="color: #2196f3; margin-bottom: 15px;">New {{userType}} Registration</h2>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 16px;">
                    A new {{userType}} has registered and requires your review for approval.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="user-profile">
                <div class="user-type-badge user-type-{{userType}}">{{userType}}</div>
                
                <div class="user-details">
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Full Name</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{fullName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Email Address</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{email}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{#if businessName}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Business Name</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{businessName}}</div>
                    </div>
                    {{/if}}
                    <div class="detail-item">
                        <div class="detail-label">Registration Date</div>
                        <div class="detail-value">{{registrationDate}}</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="action-required">
                <h4>⚡ Immediate Action Required</h4>
                <p>
                    Please review this {{userType}}'s profile and decide whether to approve or reject their application. 
                    They are waiting for your decision to access the platform.
                </p>
                
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="cta-button primary">Review Profile</a>
                    <a href="{{reviewUrl}}" class="cta-button secondary">View Details</a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="registration-summary">
                <h4>📊 Registration Summary</h4>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 15px;">
                    {{#if (eq userType 'merchant')}}
                    New business registration requires verification of business details and approval process.
                    {{else}}
                    New user registration requires profile review and membership approval.
                    {{/if}}
                </p>
                
                <div style="background: #fff3e0; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 15px 0; border-left: 4px solid #FF9933;">
                    <h5 style="color: #FF9933; margin-bottom: 10px;">📋 Review Checklist:</h5>
                    <ul style="color: #666; padding-left: 20px; margin: 0;">
                        <li>Verify email address and contact information</li>
                        {{#if (eq userType 'merchant')}}
                        <li>Check business legitimacy and documentation</li>
                        <li>Validate business address and contact details</li>
                        <li>Ensure business aligns with community guidelines</li>
                        {{else}}
                        <li>Check profile completeness and authenticity</li>
                        <li>Verify community connection and eligibility</li>
                        {{/if}}
                        <li>Review terms and conditions acceptance</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 25px 0; text-align: center;">
                <h4 style="color: #1976d2; margin-bottom: 15px;">⏰ Response Time Goal</h4>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 10px;">
                    Please review and respond within <strong>24-48 hours</strong> to maintain good user experience.
                </p>
                <p style="color: #666; font-size: 14px;">
                    Quick responses help build trust and engagement in our community.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p><strong>Indians in Ghana - Admin Dashboard</strong></p>
            <p>You're receiving this notification because you're an admin.</p>
            <p>📧 Admin Support: admin@indiansinghana.com</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
